WEBVTT

00:02:01.763 --> 00:02:03.697
And before we leave the room,

00:02:03.721 --> 00:02:06.657
we tell them not to peek at the cards.

00:02:07.518 --> 00:02:08.934
Of course,

00:02:08.958 --> 00:02:11.119
we have hidden cameras in the room

00:02:11.143 --> 00:02:12.938
to watch their every move.

00:02:14.216 --> 00:02:17.633
Because the desire
to win the game is so strong,

00:02:17.657 --> 00:02:21.143
more than 90 percent of children will peek

00:02:21.167 --> 00:02:22.604
as soon as we leave the room.

00:02:22.628 --> 00:02:24.628
(Laughter)

00:02:25.044 --> 00:02:27.030
The crucial question is:

00:02:27.054 --> 00:02:29.802
When we return and ask the children

00:02:29.826 --> 00:02:32.135
whether or not they have peeked,